---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Stats is Fun">
    <div class="animate-fade-in max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
        
        <div class="prose prose-indigo max-w-none text-slate-600">
            <p class="mb-6">
                Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}
            </p>

            <p class="mb-8">
                Thank you for using "Stats is Fun". This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information and your rights respecting that information.
            </p>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Target Audience</h2>
                <div class="bg-indigo-50 border-l-4 border-indigo-500 p-4 rounded-r-lg">
                    <p class="text-indigo-900">
                        <strong>For Everyone:</strong> This application is intended for a general audience and does not contain any mature or adult-only content. It is designed to be an educational tool for learning statistics.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Data Collection and Usage</h2>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>
                        <strong>No Personal Information Collected:</strong> We do not collect, store, or share any Personally Identifiable Information (PII) such as names, email addresses, phone numbers, or location data.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>No Data Storage:</strong> The app functions locally on your device and does not upload user data to any external servers.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Permissions and Access</h2>
                <p>
                    "Stats is Fun" respects your device's security and privacy:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-4">
                    <li>
                        <strong>No Storage Access:</strong> This app does not request or require access to your device's external storage, photos, or media files.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>No Camera/Microphone:</strong> This app does not access your camera or microphone.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Payments and Transactions</h2>
                <p>
                    <strong>Completely Free:</strong> "Stats is Fun" contains no payment mechanisms, paywalls, or in-app purchases. It is free to use for educational purposes.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Third Party Services</h2>
                <p>
                    <strong>No Third Party Services:</strong> This application does not utilize any third-party services, analytics, or tracking tools. No data is shared with external parties.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
                <p>
                    We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.
                </p>
                <p class="mt-4">
                    <strong>Permission Updates:</strong> Should there be any changes to the permissions required by the "Stats is Fun" application in the future, this Privacy Policy will be immediately updated to reflect those changes and inform you of the new requirements.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
                <p>
                    If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us.
                </p>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
